Texts.Chs: 把1份^orange;中子素和反中子素^reset;带给^red;凯文^reset;
好礼法克屑特宝，你居然做到了。我猜你还没有我想象中的那么笨。作为回报，我会把这个超级牛逼的科技蓝图交给你，这可是我在^orange;反异界^reset;找到的！不，我不会告诉你那是哪里摘到的。你不能知道，因为你不像^cyan;戴夫^reset;那样牛逼。
Texts.Eng: Holy forking shirtballs, you did it. I guess you aren't the dumbass I had assumed. In return, I give you this super-neat technology blueprint I found in the ^orange;Anti-Realm^reset;! No, I won't tell you where that is. You can't know, because you aren't special like ^cyan;Dave^reset;.

Wanna try something ^orange;super fun^reset;? Let's create something previously thought to be ^green;hypothetical^reset;! Let's try making ^orange;Neutronium^reset; and ^orange;Anti-Neutronium^reset;! I'll give you something ^red;truly amazing^reset; if you can do it! I promise. For real, this time.
Texts.Chs: 想试试这个^orange;超级有趣的东西^reset;吗？让我们创造一些以前被认为是^green;假想^reset;的东西！让我们试着做^orange;中子素^reset;和^orange;反中子素^reset;！我会给你一些^red;真正令人惊叹的东西^reset;如果你能做到话！我保证。真的，这一次。
